      "title": "This Startup Is Fixing Our Broken Food System\u2026 The Story, The Impact, The Future\u2014 Farmdrop",
      "description": "We keep hearing that the food system is \u201cbroken\u201d\u2026 but this conversation shows what fixing it actually looks like.\n\nFrom learning with farmers across Spain, Mexico, and Guatemala to leading a 15-year grassroots movement, Hannah shares how **FarmDrop** is rebuilding the connection between producers and people\u2014using tech, community, and a mission-driven model.\n\nThis isn\u2019t just about buying food.\nIt\u2019s about:\n\u2022 Giving farmers control over pricing and distribution\n\u2022 Reducing waste through smarter systems\n\u2022 Expanding access to real, local food\n\u2022 Redefining what \u201clocal\u201d truly means\n\nFarmDrop blends the simplicity of a farmers market with the power of technology\u2014creating a system where communities don\u2019t just consume food\u2026 they participate in it.\n\n\n\ud83d\udc47 Watch the full story:\n\nhttps://youtu.be/Y8ykMqUTlS4?si=rujIEK0S2POz3U8h",
